## Attribution Requirements

When using this software, you must:

1. **Credit the Creator**
   - Name: SilverBitcoin Foundation
   - Website: https://silverbitcoin.org
   - GitHub: https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/SilverBitcoin

2. **Link to License**
   - Provide a link to: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

3. **Indicate Changes**
   - If you modified the software, clearly state what changes were made
   - Example: "Based on SilverBitcoin by SilverBitcoin Foundation, modified for [purpose]"

4. **Example Attribution**
   ```
   This project uses SilverBitcoin blockchain software
   Copyright (c) 2024-2025 SilverBitcoin Foundation
   Licensed under CC BY 4.0: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
   Source: https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/SilverBitcoin
   ```

