SilverBitcoin Foundation. Use of these trademarks requires attribution as
specified above. Commercial use of trademarks may require additional permission.

### Patents
This software may be covered by patents. The CC BY 4.0 License does not grant
any patent rights beyond those necessary to use the software as licensed.

